data.description: Welcome to this charming 19th-century farmhouse nestled on 2.2 picturesque acres with beautiful country views. Property offers a unique blend of historic character & modern conveniences. Oversized 2.5 car garage has ample space for your vehicles and storage needs. Expansive covered porch with newer porch rails. Upon entering you are transported back in time, admire the preserved details that make this farmhouse truly special. The wood shutters, exposed brick walls, wood beams & built-ins add warmth throughout the home. Living room boasts a spacious layout & exudes a nice cozy feel. Focal point of this room is a beautiful wood-burning stove with white stone surround. Fall in love with your bright airy country kitchen, featuring tin backsplash, attractive lighting & stainless steel appliances. Primary bedroom has ALL the feels, brick walls, barn wood doors & en-suite room that can be tailored to your needs. Upstairs you'll find a loft & 3 additional bedrooms plus new flooring -December 2023. Outside the property continues to exceed your expectations. Witness natures magic throughout the 4 seasons with vast views of rolling farm fields. Newer fencing throughout your backyard, ready for your agricultural animals & 4-H projects! Updates- Furnace & A/C-2016, roof & radon mitigation system-2021, cellar sealed 2022
